@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Archived
Archived --> OnHold : update
OnHold --> Draft : cancel
OnHold : entry / log reservation
Draft --> Closed : update
Closed --> Rejected : process
Closed : entry / log reservation
Rejected --> Pending : reject
Pending --> [*]
@enduml